      "title": "Sri Lanka: Navy ships with unidentified persons left Colombo Port",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Reports have surfaced that luggage was rushed on to the Sri Lanka Navy Ship Gajabahu anchored at the Colombo Port.",
        "The Harbour Master at the Colombo Port said that a group boarded the SLNS Sindurala, and SLNS Gajabahu and left the port.",
        "He said he cannot provide details of the manifest or about those who boarded the vessels.",
        "<iframe src=\u201dhttps://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=476&href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNewsfirstSL%2Fvideos%2F725646241991892%2F&show_text=false&width=476&t=0\u2033 width=\u201d476\u2033 height=\u201d476\u2033 style=\u201dborder:none;overflow:hidden\u201d scrolling=\u201dno\u201d frameborder=\u201d0\u2033 allowfullscreen=\u201dtrue\u201d allow=\u201dautoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share\u201d allowFullScreen=\u201dtrue\u201d></iframe>",
